        <h2 align="center">2016-17 Memberships Now Available</h2>

        <p>LFC Raleigh is the Official Liverpool Supporters Club (OLSC) based here in the Raleigh-Durham area of North Carolina.
            Back in May 2014, we were privileged to be invited as the 210th official supporters club and we have continued to grow ever since.
            Annual memberships for the 2016-17 season are now available for only $20!!!  You may ask yourself why become a member?
            See below.  Why wouldn’t you?!?!?</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>Exclusive 2016-17 LFC Raleigh shirt</strong> (to be picked up at the pub, or it can be shipped to your home for an additional $10 fee)</li>
            <li>Voting rights at the Annual General Meeting</li>
            <li>Match-day specials at the London Bridge Pub</li>
            <li>Discount on LFC Raleigh merchandise (available at London Bridge Pub) as available</li>
            <li>Access to special events during pre-season tour activities, such as team training sessions, player meet-and-greets, and legend autograph sessions.</li>
            <li>Access to the LFC ticketing portal for home Premier League matches (note that you also must carry official LFC membership – not international membership – to take advantage of this benefit)</li>
            <li>Official membership card</li>
            <li>One free raffle ticket to win great LFC merchandise during the annual holiday party</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We are a non-profit organization.  All proceeds will be used to help subsidize food and beverage at a future LFC Raleigh event.</p>

        <p>You can pay below directly with a credit card via secure connection, or you can find us at London Bridge Pub where we have a card reader.
            LFC Raleigh will <strong>never</strong> save your credit card information.</p>

